The lentiviral vector market is projected to witness significant growth by 2030. Lentiviral vectors are widely used in various gene therapy applications due to their ability to efficiently deliver genetic material into target cells. With the increasing prevalence of genetic disorders and advancements in gene editing technologies, the demand for lentiviral vectors is expected to rise steadily over the forecast period. Additionally, the rising investments in research and development activities focused on gene therapy and personalized medicine are further driving the market growth.

